headline: GoDaddy (GDDY) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of domain registrar and web services company GoDaddy (NYSE:GDDY) fell 1.6% in the afternoon session after it continued a recent downward trend amid a period of significant underperformance.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid GDDY and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the last six months, GoDaddy’s shares have sunk to $145, producing a disappointing 18.4% loss - a stark contrast to the S&P 500’s 9.7% gain. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
